{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回\"绝世传\"摘要：芮玮独斗天地人三魔及九大蛇将，以简召舞所教三招\"惊涛拍岸\"\"滔天巨浪\"\"骇浪排空\"应战，但因功力不足无法破阵。危急时刻本能使出黑堡\"无常掌\"，引起三魔怀疑他是假公子。关键时刻芮玮施出喻百龙所传\"玄妙三十掌\"，一招各打三魔一耳光，三魔惊疑不定。此时天池府内冲出一名黑衣蒙面高手，武功极高，一掌重创芮玮。简怀萱误认黑衣人为大哥简召舞，大喊\"大哥手下留情\"。芮玮昏厥后被喻百龙救至简氏家族巨墓石室中疗伤。喻百龙耗尽精力为芮玮疗伤，自身苍老许多。得知黑堡铩羽而归，天池府仅烧毁一栋房屋。喻百龙怒斥\"不义之人\"，阻止芮玮再回天池府，并决定收芮玮为徒。喻百龙将芮玮安置在墓中最隐密的暗室中修炼，传授举世无匹的内功心法\"天衣神功\"。芮玮透露父亲芮问夫传下\"龟息大功\"，喻百龙告知两功同属玄门正宗可同时修炼。最后喻百龙得知芮玮之父正是芮问夫，大惊失色。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mo",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下哪有这等掌法，竟能出此招数！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "天魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九疑配三才，生机永不息！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_mo",
      "speaker_name": "地魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是咱们黑堡的'无常掌'。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "天魔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没想到天下顶顶大名的天池府，深藏武学奇书万卷，哪知简公子在最危急时不会使出精妙的招数解救，而仅使出本堡的'无常掌'，岂不令人可疑！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_qing_nong",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "记得咱们剑下亡魂芮玮那小子把'无常掌'练得甚熟！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "天魔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "莫非阁下还是假公子？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "天魔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "看来你在天池府倒偷学了三招！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_mo",
      "speaker_name": "地魔",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁敢来送死……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "天魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是什么掌法？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_qing_nong",
      "speaker_name": "人魔",
      "listener": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "text": "大哥……他……他……不是芮玮！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "大哥手下留情！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我芮玮死了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你还没死？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老夫的声音也听不出来吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "你是喻老前辈！你……你……怎么也来到这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我怎么不能来这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "老前辈如何去世的？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "鬼话！我喻百龙好好活着，哪里死了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "老前辈，晚辈没有死？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "假若你再不好好睡下去，不死也要落得终身残废。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不要再胡思乱想，注意啦！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你的内功不错嘛！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈自幼练先父传下的内功心法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "令尊名讳是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "先父芮……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好好睡吧！不要说了……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "前辈好！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "身体可好了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "真不中用，为了给你疗伤，这一天来总觉累得很！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈该死！害得前辈身体受害，这……这……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "别责备自己，我的身体早就觉得不中用了，怎能怪你！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "前天我见天池府火光冲天，械斗喊杀声隐隐传来，我本下定决心不进天池府，那时却顾不得了，飞快奔出森林看个究竟，到时也好暗中帮助，哪知……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "老前辈怎么啦？老前辈怎么啦？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你是个好孩子！但他却是心肠狠毒的坏孩子……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不要管他是谁，总之亏得我出来救了你，只要迟一步不但要气死我，而且遗憾终生……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈被黑衣蒙面人打昏过去，便不知一切，后来怎么啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "黑堡虽然有备而来，内外夹攻，人数又多，但是天池府个个武功不弱，他们不是对手，铩羽而归！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "真的吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我怎会骗你，天池府只被烧毁一栋房屋，黑堡本想窃取天池府的武学秘藉，结果连屁也没得到，他们哪知天池府三代聚集的武学奇书，全部藏在这里！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "她……她们都没事吗……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我救了你，见黑堡的人敌斗不过一一退走。便不管那些乱七八糟的事，也不知他们是否有人受伤！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "老前辈，晚辈出去看看她们……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不要去！以后你不用再到天池府去了……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "但是恩公要晚辈……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你何必再装扮他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈忠人所托，不得不……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么忠人所托！不准去就是不准去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不该对你发脾气，实在是对那种不义之人，用不着守信，要知江湖的事千变万化，倘若不会应变，迟早要吃大亏，你心很好，但要记着这点，要随机应变，古来不少愚忠的大将，就因不能应变，结果功不成，身先死，那是多不值得的事！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你就住在这里罢！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈住在这里做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你可跟我学艺？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈愿学！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我的武功十分难学，而且学会后，要有极大的毅力为我办一件事，你自认能够吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈不知自己有多大的毅力，但晚辈只记着一点，凡事诚心而为，无不可为，也无不可破！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好志气！起来吧！喻百龙竭尽所能，将一生所学传授给你。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这前面是墓中最大的一间石室，你以后就在这里练习内功武术，直到我认为满意的一天再出墓！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这里虽然没有光线，却有充足的空气流通，你住在这里，专心习练，别的什么也不用管，我自会照料。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈就住在这暗黑的石室内，不用火光？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "常人练功因有昼夜之分，往往苦苦练来只得事倍功半之数，而今你住在这里，没有昼夜之分，练累了就休息，休息好了就勤练，如此心理上觉得永在练功，不会懈怠，练一分功夫就得一分功夫，比起常人练功就强多了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈看不见前辈，如何向前辈学艺？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "任何武功，最重要的是内功，我先传你内功心法，再传武技，至于内功心法，只要知道口诀就可以。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "不知老前辈要传什么内功心法。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这内功心法我也没练过，但我深知其效力大过任何内功心法，可说举世无其匹敌，名字叫天衣神功。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天衣神功，好奇怪的名字！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "天衣神功！天衣神功！这名字虽然奇怪，却害得不少武林豪士，寐梦以求，喻某何幸，能记得其口诀。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "前辈为什么不练天衣神功？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我因自己从小习得别种内功心法，便不易再学天衣神功，故而未学！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "晚辈也练了几年内功心法，不知可易再学天衣神功。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "令尊传你什么内功心法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "先父说那内功心法，是龟息大功。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "龟息大功，这功练来甚难，我曾听过。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "先父临去世时，传了我几句口诀，晚辈盲目揣测习练数年，也不知练得对不对？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "照理说，龟息大功练成，在功力上一般内功心法绝非其敌，大成者可为江湖一流高手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "看来晚辈没练对，前天对敌时，晚辈曾打到敌人数掌，却无法将他们震伤，若然练成便不会如此了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你虽然没有练到大成的效果，也已经略有成效，只要好好努力下去，不难练得大成。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "习练了龟息大功可能再习天衣神功？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这两种内功心法，都是玄门正宗，不相克犯，可同时练成，你既有了龟息大功的底子，再练天衣神功，成效比仅练天衣神功，要高得多了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我想起来了！令尊是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "text": "先父讳字问夫。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "喻百龙",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "果真是他！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    }
  ],
